name: "Abstract (11 June 2021 - C)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Ballpoint pen and packing tape on canvas book cover with digital embellishments and color.] It's abstract---meaning that the concept isn't condensed into a unified, visually recognizable image. The point here is mystery and insinuation. Can you GUESS what it means? (If so, then YES, that's what it means........to you!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
